node.text:
Proper Peaches 🍑🥃 @thenotoriousmma @justinbieber 

2 parts Proper No. Twelve Irish Whiskey
1/2 part simple syrup
1 peach, diced
3-4 mint leaves
Splash of soda water

Muddle peaches, simple syrup & mint leaves in a shaker
Add Proper No. Twelve and fill shaker with ice
Strain into rocks glass over fresh ice
Top with a splash of soda water
Garnish with mint leaves and a peach slice
